.entry-header
About Us
Our Company
Who We Are
About Us
Our mission is to create a homely and supportive community in which our residents can live in health and well-being both physically and socially. We know very well that retirement is a way for you to do what you always wanted to, create new friends, and find a new meaning. This is why we put amenities and activities that promote an active and socially involved living into the design of our community.
Contact Us
Our Mission
At Colonial Mobile Home Park, our mission is:
To form a lively and cohesive community in which our residents can achieve their best.
To ensure the best quality, properly maintained facilities and amenities to assist a relaxing and pleasurable living.
To offer a variety of social and recreational activities addressing diverse preferences among our residents.
To comprehensively consider the health, security, and well-being of the community members.
We aim to constantly up our game for senior living, setting the bar for an unforgettable 55+ community.
Home Is Where You
Park It
Welcome to Colonial Mobile Home Park – a 55+ seniors’ community that provides everything you need to lead a comfortable life, but with a twist of a resort-style life.
Contact Us
